5
00:02:16,519 --> 00:02:19,619
 Cherry, wipe the drool off your desk. 

6
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:24,219
 Lin Qi Le! Lin Qi Le! 

7
00:02:24,219 --> 00:02:27,600
Lin Qi Le, wake up!

8
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:40,440
- What's wrong? 
 - Teacher Wang wants you in the office.

9
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:42,560
Your mom is here.

10
00:02:43,460 --> 00:02:47,299
 Lin Qi Le's mom, you must watch over her. 

11
00:02:47,299 --> 00:02:49,000
 She is a promising young talent. 

12
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,219
 Why can't she focus on her studies? 

13
00:02:51,219 --> 00:02:54,099
 She is a first-year-high school student. 
 School has already started for several days. 

14
00:02:54,099 --> 00:02:58,099
 College entrance exams are near, 
 yet she is still writing letters in class. 

15
00:02:58,099 --> 00:03:00,219
 Several teachers reported this to me. 

16
00:03:00,219 --> 00:03:03,939
 Children at this stage 
 lack the motivation to learn. 

17
00:03:03,939 --> 00:03:05,740
 As parents, you should take the initiative. 

18
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:07,499
 Teacher, you are right. 

19
00:03:07,499 --> 00:03:10,219
 Please try harder in the future. 

20
00:03:10,219 --> 00:03:11,339
 I'm leaving then. 

21
00:03:11,339 --> 00:03:15,140
 Fine. We will be in touch. 

22
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:17,019
 - Teacher Wang, there's no need to see me off. 
 - All right. 

23
00:03:17,019 --> 00:03:18,980
 Thank you. 

24
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,659
Let's go.

25
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:50,659
Cherry, if you still want to write those letters, 
 do it at home.

26
00:03:50,659 --> 00:03:53,619
Mom, there's nothing wrong 
 with writing those letters.

27
00:03:53,619 --> 00:03:58,520
Still, if it's done during class, 
 it affects classroom discipline.

28
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,960
Mom,

29
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:06,360
am I a very… strange child?

30
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:09,220
I always make you and Dad worry.

31
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:21,079
I'm sorry, dear. 
 You should be with your friends,

32
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:25,640
but now you're all alone in Qunshan.

33
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,940
What are you talking about? Me alone?

34
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:33,619
I have you and Dad! 
 I have the whole Qunshan!

35
00:04:33,619 --> 00:04:35,648
I can't be without you even for a moment!

36
00:04:35,648 --> 00:04:38,679
I want to be Qunshan's last guardian!

37
00:04:38,679 --> 00:04:39,739
Really?

38
00:04:39,739 --> 00:04:41,239
Really.

39
00:04:50,339 --> 00:04:52,050
Cherry,

40
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:54,570
you're growing up.

41
00:04:54,579 --> 00:04:57,279
Growing up is a process 
 of breaking out of one's shell.

42
00:04:57,279 --> 00:05:02,700
If you keep dwelling on the past, 
 you'll suffocate.

43
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:06,419
People and emotions are both fluctuating.

44
00:05:06,419 --> 00:05:09,700
If you keep dwelling on the past 
 and past events,

45
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:12,479
it's natural to feel unhappy.

46
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:24,340
Does letting go of the past completely,

47
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:28,619
as if nothing had ever happened,

48
00:05:28,619 --> 00:05:33,720
mean that someone is doing well now?

49
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:41,060
I don't know how others are doing,

50
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:47,059
but I know you're not doing well.

51
00:05:57,620 --> 00:06:02,099
Letters only exist as letters 
 when they're sent.

52
00:06:02,099 --> 00:06:06,419
The ones kept with you are only knots.

53
00:06:16,339 --> 00:06:20,099
 Jiang Qiao Xi, the construction site 
 is almost complete. 

54
00:06:20,099 --> 00:06:24,440
 The three water cooling towers 
 no longer shine at night. 

55
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:28,500
 Sometimes I wonder, 
 if you come back to Qunshan at night 

56
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:33,480
 and can't see their lights, will you get lost? 

57
00:06:34,799 --> 00:06:38,759
 Jiang Qiao Xi, salvia is so sweet-flavored. 

58
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:42,099
 I've always wanted to save some for you. 

59
00:06:42,099 --> 00:06:46,000
 If we meet one day in the summer, 

60
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:49,160
 I'll come see you with a bunch of salvias. 

61
00:06:49,979 --> 00:06:53,380
 Jiang Qiao Xi, 
 it's been five years since we met. 

62
00:06:53,380 --> 00:06:56,460
 How are you? 

63
00:06:56,460 --> 00:07:00,260
 Chun Lu died a few days ago. 

64
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:03,979
 Back then, we had agreed 
 that she was your daughter, 

65
00:07:03,979 --> 00:07:08,179
 so I think I should write to let you know. 

66
00:07:08,179 --> 00:07:12,000
 I buried her on the mountaintop 
 where we watched the sunset together. 

67
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,900
 You are those vibrant sunsets. 

68
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:18,959
 This way, she can always be with her father. 

69
00:08:00,799 --> 00:08:02,659
Hello.

70
00:08:02,659 --> 00:08:03,999
 Lin Cherry, it's me. 

71
00:08:03,999 --> 00:08:06,979
Qin Ye Yun, 
 why are you calling me so early?

72
00:08:06,979 --> 00:08:11,820
Lin Cherry, did you write a huge letter 
 to Jiang Qiao Xi?

73
00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:12,900
How did you know?

74
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:16,660
Didn't I tell you not to contact him again?

75
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:20,900
Why?

76
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:25,659
Does he still not have time 
 to read my letter?

77
00:08:25,659 --> 00:08:28,439
Who cares if he's busy? You two are different!

78
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:31,219
Don't ever think about this person again. 
 Don't mention him at all.

79
00:08:31,219 --> 00:08:35,180
- Tell her the truth! She can't… 
 - What truth?

80
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:39,539
Qin Ye Yun, what is going on? 
 Did something happen?

81
00:08:39,539 --> 00:08:41,860
Don't ask! 
 In any case, don't contact him again!

82
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,660
You're not allowed to!

83
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:47,330
Wait! You…

84
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:52,480
 Jiang Qiao Xi! 

85
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:55,899
 Jiang Qiao Xi! Jiang Qiao Xi! 

86
00:09:55,899 --> 00:09:59,459
 You must write to me! You must write to me! 

87
00:09:59,459 --> 00:10:03,179
 Cherry, I'll be back after the winter break! 

88
00:10:03,179 --> 00:10:07,000
 Cherry, I'll be back after the winter break! 

89
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:12,380
 I know that no matter how brave I am, 

90
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:14,236
 I can't grow wings. 

