♫  I gaze intently from afar  ♫

95
00:10:26,101 --> 00:10:28,444
♫  Unspoken wishes of that year  ♫

96
00:10:28,444 --> 00:10:31,671
♫  Your familiar shadow stretches further  ♫

97
00:10:31,671 --> 00:10:34,855
♫  Beyond my sight  ♫ 
 ♫  Your silhouette appears so gentle  ♫

98
00:10:34,855 --> 00:10:37,579
 Girl! Girl! 

99
00:10:37,579 --> 00:10:41,939
Do you get car sick? Orange peel can help.

100
00:10:41,939 --> 00:10:43,232
Thank you.

101
00:10:43,232 --> 00:10:47,375
♫  The gentle breeze carries my shouts away  ♫

